@*
    Home-page tile content.

    Rendered by the host inside the <button> it owns for launching this game
    from the home page. Keep it visual — artwork, typography, animations — so
    players can tell it apart from other tiles. Click handling, disabled state,
    aria-label, and tile sizing come from the host's button, not from here.

    Style via this component's scoped CSS (MyGameTile.razor.css), which ships
    as part of wwwroot/MyGame.styles.css and is served from
    /_content/MyGame/MyGame.styles.css by the platform.
*@
